Package com.flipfit.bean

Class GymOwner

java.lang.Object
com.flipfit.bean.GymOwner
public class GymOwner extends Object
The GymOwner class represents a gym owner user in the FlipFit system. It contains specific details for a gym owner, such as their unique user ID and business-related identification numbers like PAN, Aadhaar, and GST.

      public GymOwner(int userId, String pan, String aadhaar, String gst)
      Constructs a new GymOwner object. This constructor is used during the registration process for a new gym owner, where the profile is not yet approved.
      Parameters:
      userId - The unique ID of the user.
      pan - The PAN number of the gym owner.
      aadhaar - The Aadhaar number of the gym owner.
      gst - The GST number of the gym.

    • GymOwner

      public GymOwner(int userId, String pan, String aadhaar, String gst, boolean isApproved)
      Constructs a GymOwner object with a pre-existing approval status. This constructor is typically used when retrieving an existing gym owner's details from the database.
      Parameters:
      userId - The unique ID of the user.
      pan - The PAN number of the gym owner.
      aadhaar - The Aadhaar number of the gym owner.
      gst - The GST number of the gym.
      isApproved - The approval status of the owner.
